SAMCHAT 0.4 for Linux

1. Uses select() system call which reduces computer resource utilization when blocking system calls are encountered in both server and client...

2. Removed bugs:
	* If remote server terminates... clients are indicated...

	* Offline messages can be sent with notifications

	* The ncurses is changed to present screen for varying size of both GUI terminal (pseudo terminal) & text terminal (tty)

